---
title: Pan-Seared Fish Sandwich with Roasted Potatoes and Lemony Dip
description: Forget about fish Fridays! This revamped fish sandwich, flavoured with a lemony sauce and paired with dill-dusted potatoes, is totally craveable any day of the week.
